headline: Royal Caribbean vs. Carnival: Which cruise stock to own? Bernstein answers
summary: Investing.com -- Bernstein analysts initiated coverage on the cruise industry, giving Royal Caribbean (NYSE:RCL) an Outperform rating while assigning Carnival (NYSE:CCL) a Market-Perform rating in a note Tuesday.
